data.description: Welcome to 133 Southgate Ct., a private residence nestled within the highly desired community of The Colony in Pawleys Island.  Built in 2016, this well-maintained residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and coastal elegance.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed floor plan that maximizes both space and functionality. The main level boasts three generously sized bedrooms, providing convenience and accessibility. Each room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  The heart of the home is undoubtedly the spacious kitchen, a culinary haven for both aspiring chefs and family gatherings. With modern appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry, this kitchen is as practical as it is aesthetically pleasing.  The two-car garage ensures that your vehicles are sheltered from the elements, while the fenced yard adds an extra layer of privacy and security. Whether you have children and pets or simply enjoy outdoor living, the fenced yard offers a tranquil space to relax and unwind.  Pawleys Island itself is renowned for its pristine beaches, charming shops, award-winning golf courses and delicious dining options, providing a coastal lifestyle that's second to none. Don't miss the opportunity to make this 2016-built gem your home. With its ideal location, spacious interior, and modern amenities, this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence in The Colony is ready to welcome you into the coastal lifestyle you've been dreaming of.
